title: Any news on new champ select for OCE?

replies.body:
Riot are planning to have NA and TR trial the new champion select over the next 3 days, after that (if all goes well) it should be rolled out in the following days. (after the 17th) 

Oce should have the new champion select by the time ranked resets. (January 20th 00:00AM AEST)
Did i miss something or are the tests just not going well?

> [{quoted}](name=Rdiggity,realm=OCE,application-id=Ntey9fRZ,discussion-id=XWZPXLxy,comment-id=00000001,timestamp=2016-01-19T16:46:44.607+0000)
>
> Did i miss something or are the tests just not going well?

I believe there have been some issues with the tests. Not sure on what or how bad though.
Thanks! I've been wondering why we don't have it yet.
